The aftermath of breaking generational curses. 👏🏾⁠
⁠
"Mothering Phee is healing in and of itself but this little moment definitely was special ❤️ my little goofy goober’s just frolicking through life and I love it.⁠
⁠
One thing I’m realizing in parenting her is that so much of the ease and joy in motherhood has come, not through molding her behavior to be convenient for me but through preserving her innocence by handling her gently." - @destini.ann⁠
